{"tid":2219605,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"前暴雪創辦人另起爐灶   開新遊戲公司 Dreamhaven","createTime":"2020-09-27T04:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T13:19:46.000Z","uid":105678,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cb2561705c545425689a4da2777b2dc3e32dbaa3","tid":2219605,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/777d9ac665632da6e457dcb33ebf709b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F777d9ac665632da6e457dcb33ebf709b.jpeg&h=9c26181b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暴雪創辦人兼總裁的 Mike Morhaime 在 2018 年時宣布退休，惟最近決定重出江湖，與暴雪一眾前資深研發成員合作成立新的遊戲公司 Dreamhaven。<br />\n<br />\n根據《gamesindusty.biz》報導，Dreamhaven 總部取址與暴雪一樣，座落在加州爾灣市。而 Dreamhaven 將作為提供資金與意見的遊戲母公司，而開發工作則交給旗下品牌工作室 Moonshot 和  Secret Door ，兩個工作室目前正各自開發不同的新遊戲。<br />\n<br />\nDreamhaven 現時的員工大多為前暴雪員工，如 Moonshot 工作室的就是由早期製作《爐石戰記》以及《星海爭霸2》 的 Jason Chayes、《暴雪英霸》遊戲總監 Dustin Browder，和前《爐石戰記》創意總監 Ben Thompson 共同領導；而 Secret Door 工作室的負責人則是由前暴雪副總裁之一的 Chris Sigaty 、《爐石戰記》首任遊戲總監 Eric Dodds 和《暴雪英霸》總監 Alan Dabiri 擔任。<br />\n<br />\n而 Mike Morhaime 表示，他很高興能與這群充滿才華的人合作，並永遠相信在遊戲中有股力量可以讓玩家不受背景與疆域限制而聚集在一起，希望可以透過 Dreamhaven 與各地玩家共同創造與分享新的遊戲體驗。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：gamesindusty.biz"},{"pid":"6b56c8eb3fcaae15d79c01bedd4e4cfdd7c8be32","tid":2219605,"uid":36995,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:09:17.000Z","msg":"做肥左=被中國收購"},{"pid":"5788653e447dafa0cdd711a0eb995eda6c753fe3","tid":2219605,"uid":3534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:15:48.000Z","msg":"點都好，唔係俾中資入就得"},{"pid":"a1f38e9507a5941e1c335c9672f9f408b76c744c","tid":2219605,"uid":35155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:58:41.000Z","msg":"砌低共雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ce93281d400c99458072756874aa845b8a9e9e","tid":2219605,"uid":171310,"like